        "answer_count": 2,
        "title": "is it possible to use a java array in javascript function?",
        "body": "<p>Im trying to pass an array of strings from a java servlet to a jsp file.\nnow, i want to use that array in a javascript function in that same jsp file.\nis this possible?<\/p>\n",
        "question_id": 22028290,
        "tags": [
            "java",
            "javascript",
            "jsp",
            "servlets",
            "model-view-controller"
        ],
        "score": 1,
